title: Dillon 650XL User Guide.iso
description: The Dillon Precision electronic user guide includes expert step-by-step instructions for unpacking, assembling, setting up, and safely operating your XL 650. This hybrid DVD features detail close-up, and our exclusive reloads' view camera angles as well as bonus content for use on your home computer. Simply place this disc in any computer with a DVD drive for printable documentation, handy web links and a reloading log book. This electronic user guide also covers many optional accessories and will help you quickly get started and on your way to safely enjoying your new reloading machine
